email login
-
1. login me email ginete api call sto mobile url me email kai password
2. redirect to the page the popup was opened with session / cookie


phone login
-
1. login me tilefono ginete api call sto mobile url me ton arithmo tilefonou
2. vgenei to popup gia to otp kai ginete call sto url me to otp
3. redirect to the page the popup was opened with session / cookie

social login
-
1. login me social
2. meta to succesfull login kanei redirect sto page me ta data apo fb/google
- https://www.delivery.gr/login/process/facebook
- https://www.delivery.gr/login/process/google
3. redirect to the page the popup was opened with session / cookie


Tha yparxei mia selida eite server side eite me js modal gia to verify ton stoixeion.
tha valouyme log-out se afti ti selida?
To pou htan o xristis prin kanei login tha apothikevete sto session (server side)


