3. deixnw to modal me to new user details
4. o xristis pataei panw sto input phone
5. grafei to noumero k pataei to btn
6. ginete ena call sto api me to VERIFYNUMBER me to tilefono tou xristi pros eggrafi
7. deixnoume to modal me to otp
8. o xristis vazei to otp kai ginete ena call sto VERIFYNUMBER me to otp
9. o xristis pataei sto koumpi dimiourgia logariasmou afou ola eiani ok
10. ginete call sto register api REGISTER




