TIMESLOTS
---------------
otan i diefthinsi p exeis den eksipiretite apo to katastima kai eisai se delivery method:
- on page load: na kokinisoume to selected address kai na valoume to keimeno.
- on page load na vgaloume b level alert: den upostirizete to address.
- on click se product modal add to cart btn:
 na vgaloume b level alert: den upostirizete to address. to koumpi na einai fake disabled kai na patiete.



Delivery only
-----
Sto apply na ginei call sto endpoint
{
storeID: storeid
type delivery
date 2020-03-01
from: 10:00
to: 12:00
id: 1
}
ta data mesa sto modal tha ginoun render server side.
on page load tha epilego to selected apo to context head


Delivery and pickup
-----
Sto apply na ginei call sto endpoint

{
storeID: storeid
type delivery
date 2020-03-01
from: 10:00
to: 12:00
id: 1
type pickup
date 2020-03-01
from: 10:00
to: 12:00
id: 1
}

on page load
ta data mesa sto modal tha ginoun render server side.
on page load tha epilego to selected apo to context head
me kathe epilogi delivery timeslot, ginete call sto api gia na parw ta pickup dates/timeslots

api gia na parw ta pickup dates/timeslots
---
/delivery-slots
{
storeID: storeid
date 2020-03-01
from: 10:00
to: 12:00
id: 1
}

